{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0020","text":"興建加速沒落","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["時間流逝","興衰"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["興建","加速","沒落"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,3,3,2,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hing1","gin3","gaa1","cuk1","mut6","lok6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"興建","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"加速","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"沒落","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「興建加速沒落」與「歡笑加速寂寞」結構相似，描繪了事物發展的迅速和衰敗的不可避免。"},"source":{"title":"結束開始","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4457","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0021","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0021","text":"旅途終結 全是大峽谷","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["生命終結","絕望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["旅途","終結","大峽谷"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,0,3,4,0,2,2,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["leoi5","tou4","zung1","git3","cyun4","si6","daai6","haap6","guk1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"旅途","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"終結","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"全是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"大峽谷","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「旅途終結，全是懸崖」用極端的意象，表達了生命走到盡頭的絕望和虛無。"},"source":{"title":"結束開始","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4457","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0022","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0022","text":"誰能停留 高峯上慶祝","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["時間流逝","對生命的質疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["停留","高峯","慶祝"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,0,3,3,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","nang4","ting4","lau4","gou1","fung1","hing3","zuk1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"停留","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"高峯","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"上","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"慶祝","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「誰能停留高峯上慶祝」反問，表達了對生命短暫、無法享受成功的無奈。"},"source":{"title":"結束開始","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4457","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0023","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0023","text":"送我搭上 方舟","structure":{"line_index":23,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["逃避","尋求庇護"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["方舟"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,4,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["sung3","ngo5","daap3","fong1","zau1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"送","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"搭","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"上","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"方舟","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「送我搭上方舟」是一個比喻，暗示希望找到一個避難所來逃避現實的痛苦。"},"source":{"title":"結束開始","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4457","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0022","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_NDQ1Nw_0024","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
